It is euro 5 but I have only tested it with english setting.

Just put this folder into the PSP/Game directory. 
I have tested it on 3.71 33m-3 custom firmware and It should 
work upto 3.8 33m-5 firmware. 
Not sure on firmware lower or higher than this so you will have to try it for yourself.

PPP.
